summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 69W, Page 165, of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300) to rezone certain property in Section 25, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W.M. from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone.
